{"tid":565454,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"（本土特色）新春霸街 食署唔拉 南亞小販 攻陷中環","createTime":"2018-02-19T03:57:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-19T04:56:10.000Z","uid":19552,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8d5091bd878d35b9579b4786c418b799c12a95e","tid":565454,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:57:40.000Z","msg":"南亞小販兵團攻陷中環，大發新年財！南亞裔無牌小販近日趁農曆新年長假期群起出動，本報記者連日直擊發現，近二百檔南亞小販霸佔中區數條街道和行人天橋，擺賣冒牌物品，以每檔賺近萬元計，小販兵團日賺可逾百萬元。兵團更以多輛貨車作「流動貨倉」，方便小販補給貨品。人群令巴士無法埋站，行人逼行馬路，附近商戶直指「情況失控」，令生意大跌八成，恐快要結業收場，炮轟食環署塞責，議員擔心無牌擺賣問題進一步影響當區治安，損害本港旅遊之都形象！<br />\n「Cheap（平）！Cheap（平）！」南亞小販在中環不斷向外傭兜售貨物，記者在農曆大年初一及初二直擊發現，近二百檔南亞小販兵團由早上八時起已殺到，在天橋及行人路攤開載滿貨物的行李篋，兜售冒牌手袋、衣履和電話配件等，售價介乎五至五十元不等，吸引大批外傭光顧，令上址淪為冒牌貨散貨場。人群塞爆港鐵出入口，其中干諾道中、畢打街、德輔道中及交易廣場行人天橋一帶同告淪陷。有輪椅人士及推嬰兒車的家長未能使用行人天橋的升降機，需「兜路」到環球大廈及交易廣場另覓出路。"},{"pid":"d144e7aa5f0ddf7c1e7fdf8e74ddf0b43c98f550","tid":565454,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T03:58:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180219/photo/0219-00174-001b1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180219%2Fphoto%2F0219-00174-001b1.jpg&h=152e33ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180219/photo/0219-00174-001b2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180219%2Fphoto%2F0219-00174-001b2.jpg&h=9ba1340d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180219/photo/0219-00174-001b4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180219%2Fphoto%2F0219-00174-001b4.jpg&h=5dce3d8a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/news/20180219/photo/0219-00174-001b5.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20180219%2Fphoto%2F0219-00174-001b5.jpg&h=91643d14&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a061769b9ba7ff51b21b974b79a62e7eb64c9ee2","tid":565454,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:11:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db537807f17b823659e298272598bdd9008ec76f","tid":565454,"uid":55533,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:13:37.000Z","msg":"都唔係第一年既事啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile3.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ec201cb93c9563a60620dce2bf7c3fecfd6e47e","tid":565454,"uid":13067,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:15:13.000Z","msg":"支持本土小店<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"55fc36f5076c30220cd7d9f29a6a36c94903b44e","tid":565454,"uid":29314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:15:33.000Z","msg":"中環小販問題個個星期日都有架喎。"},{"pid":"3463e156be7003059a8297d6417a69f683c840db","tid":565454,"uid":99805,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:25:33.000Z","msg":"依法辦事適用對象：本土派，本地人"},{"pid":"8281aaba976f3a439b840b01d587c388f58d53f4","tid":565454,"uid":41508,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-19T04:56:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}